data.description: Welcome to your new retreat in Madera Acres! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home has solar and dual pane windows for energy efficiency and is nestled on an oversized lot of just over 17,000 square feet. It offers a perfect blend of comfort and relaxation. The home is move-in ready with fresh interior and exterior paint. The master bedroom offers both convenience and comfort with its walk-in closet and private bathroom featuring a walk-in shower. The spacious backyard is complete with a swimming pool and covered patio space perfect for entertaining friends and family. In addition, it's conveniently located near brand new Matilda Torres High School as well as Madera Golf and Country Club and plenty of shopping options. Don't miss your chance to make it yours!
